types ContentSetting

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veepoo.protocol.model.settings.ContentSetting
  • Directly Known Subclasses:
    ContentPhoneSetting, ContentSmsSetting, ContentSocailSetting

    public abstract class ContentSetting
extends java.lang.Object
    Notification settings sent to the watch, it contains three typesContentSmsSetting,ContentPhoneSetting,ContentSocailSetting;

    ContentSmsSetting Use this class when sending content

    ContentPhoneSetting Use this class when sending phone content

    ContentSocailSetting Send to third partyAppuse this class

    Created by timaimee on 2017/6/21.
